com.axonivy.jmx

Annotation Type MComposite


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=TYPE)
 @Inherited
public @interface MComposite

    Use this annotation on classes that are used as complex attribute types. Use MItem to define the items of the complex value.

    Exmaple: 
       @MBean
  public class MyBean
  {
     @MAttribute
    private Complex complex;
  }

   @MComposite
  public class Complex
  {
     @MItem
    private String name;

     @MItem
    private String getDesription()
    {
      return "desc";
    }
  }
    Since:
    28.06.2013
    Author:
    rwei
